HEADWORD: Nodosity
<hw>No*dos"i*ty</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>nodositas</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of being
knotty or nodose; resemblance to a node or swelling; knottiness.</def>
<rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A knot; a node.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

